                "body": "Built quality is very good full aluminum casing and RCA out are gold plated. Yes it comes only with a USB C cable. No surprise it doesn’t comes with a USB power adaptor. At this price don’t expect it please. I paired mine with a linear power supply Topping P50 5V 1A plugged with an Audioquest NRGZ3 power cable to get the performance of this dac. It would be better with a 5V 2.5A linear power supply to getter better dynamics. I only use the optical & coaxial and will NEVER use the USB as input because of PC that will always generate noise. The sound quality from both optical & coaxial are very airy and has layers. You can pinpoint the singer in the middle of the two speakers. It doesn’t play ONLY in the middle but it images the true source of vocal and images the right location of the singer. That’s the beauty of this dac is it’s depth that it provides and takes it to another level. I was very surprised with it. Mid performance is great. Soundstage is very wide. Bass performance is really good not shallow and dry. At this price point you’ll fool your audio enthusiast friends. I could not believe my ears when I first plugged it to my main system and it is here to stay. Give it some time to settle Never switch it off. My conclusion is if you intend to use it with a cheap power supply you won’t get the best out of it. Get at least a linear power supply 5v 2.5A to unleash the full dynamics of this dac. At this price point and the overall performance this dac just sets the bar very high! Read more",
